01/25/2014
release
1. make certificate (once)
    keytool -genkey -v -keystore my-release-key.keystore -alias dalvikus -keyalg RSA -keysize 2048 -validity 10000 -dname "CN=Gwang-Ho KIM, OU=Android, O=DN2Soft, L=San Diego, ST=CA, C=US"
2. sign and align (always)
    jarsigner -verbose -sigalg SHA1withRSA -digestalg SHA1 -keystore my-release-key.keystore -signedjar bin/DickA-release-signed.apk bin/DickA-release-unsigned.apk dalvikus
    zipalign -f -v 4 bin/DickA-release-signed.apk bin/DickA-release.apk

